STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Earl T. MOORE, a/k/a "B," Tremaine T. Muhammad, Tremayne Taylor, Tremayne E. Moore, Stacey Moore, Tremayne Cox, Moore Cox and Subor Harris, Defendant-Petitioner. C-986 September Term 2017
080725 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 22, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004674-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
